Best practice summary

Use:

hf auth login

with a:

fine-grained read-only token

Then verify with:

hf auth whoami

Then cache the models once.

Avoid pasting the token into:

Python scripts
SPSS syntax files
PowerShell runner files
Word docs
emails
Teams messages

The token is a tiny passport. Let it live in the Hugging Face cache, not taped to the front door.
